I'll try to be a good citizen about fixing bugs and helping you use it and I really do hope you like it.

Note that:

All trademarked names mentioned in this document and SOFTWARE are used for editorial purposes only, with no intention of infringing upon the trademarks.

        </Run>
        <LineBreak />
        <LineBreak />
        <Run>
        And with that, thanks for reading!  I can't believe you made it this far.
      
        </Run>

</TextBlock>
